new file mode 100644
index 0000000..fec1e50
--- /dev/null
+++ b/.cursor/rules/python.mdc
@@ -0,0 +1,22 @@
+---
+description: Making changes to application logic
+globs: *.py
+alwaysApply: false
+---
+
+# Reference architecture
+
+1. Check [architecture.md](mdc:docs/architecture.md) for reference to make sure you are making changes in the right places
+
+# Update architecture
+
+1. If responsibilities of files or modules changes, update the [architecture.md](mdc:docs/architecture.md)
+2. If new python files or modules are introduced, update the [architecture.md](mdc:docs/architecture.md)
+
+# Coding style
+
+1. Make sure code has high cohesion and low coupling through:
+ - Favor composition (eg. through dependency injection) over inheritance
+ - Favor pure functions over state mutation
+
+Goal fo the abocve is to keep the code easy to reson about and easy to test


